      • getTaskWorkItemsForImport

        public static java.util.Map<java.lang.Integer,TWorkItemBean> getTaskWorkItemsForImport(java.lang.Integer entityID,
                                                                       int entityType)
        Gets the existing workItem tasks as a workItemID based map Get all workItems which have MSProjectTask correspondents and are of type Task. No matter that they are deleted/archived/closed (can be that they should be undeleted by returning to an earlier state by importing an older MS Project file which still contains some tasks which were set as deleted by a previous import of a newer MS project File ) We are interested just in Tasks, so if a Task's issue type is changed to something else then it is not recognized any more as existing Task by import even if it have MSProjectTask correspondents
        Parameters:
        entityID -
        entityType -
        Returns:
